verbose_text: Higher expression of MMP 2 and MMP 9 in cholesteatoma tissue in comparison to the normal canal skin was proved by many authors and by the use of different techniques such as enzyme linked immunosorbent assay, zymography, immunofluorescence, IHC, and reverse transcription-polymerase chain reaction for gene expression [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
